data.description: Welcome to Rivanna Woods where the living is easy.  Enjoy this brick one level manor home on 10 acres including water frontage on the large stocked pond with your own dock.  Sweeping veranda off of the living room and owners bedroom with views of the water and the horses below. This home features rich red oak-tile-marble flooring throughout.  Beautiful plantation shutters on the windows.  Enjoy the additional living space in the finished walk out basement.  There are several fenced paddock areas along with two barn buildings, run in and garden shed.  The community also offers a pole barn for our gatherings as well as finishing in the pond or float and relax in your canoe and kayak.
